Before you can begin editing, you must **activate your wiki account**.

To activate your account, you may fulfill **one** of these measures:

* Post your username on [this](https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=1025908.0) BitcoinTalk thread
* Join [this](https://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=bitcoin-wiki&uio=d4) IRC channel and ask directly
* Send the wiki an arbitrary fee [here](Special:CryptoPayment) and become an editor automatically
